text: Drago Jelić (16 November 1914 - 11 December 1990) was a Yugoslav gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:1990 deaths Category:Yugoslav male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
